{
  "stem": "23832.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I'm as a [INAUDIBLE] off that line in the house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And it was, I felt-- I felt something bit me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I was tending by the dining table.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And-- and it was red.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I thought, uh-oh.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It must be infected, and I'll probably get it-- trouble, that infection.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I counted two weeks, and I was scared to death.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "In meantime, the Red Cross-- I don't know-- International Red Cross was--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I married him in the--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the ghetto was on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What happened?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were-- [PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] I already that time passed my state board test, and I was working.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In one day, you see on the walls, placards or announcements-- I know what you call it-- that [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Dr.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Czerniakow, who was the head of the Warsaw ghetto engineer-- [PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] how do we say in English-- [NON-ENGLISH]-- honored-- honored hi-- to his memory.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He tragically died.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What happened, the Germans called in, and they said, in those years, everybody who was somebody and had the money, they would buy cyanide.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In case comes a situation that there no way out, they rather take the cyanide than go to-- taken by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he had this cyanide.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When he received that call-- but every day, you have to deliver so many to the Germans-- he said, I have [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He put the receiver down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he decided that he has not anybody to give away to them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He's not going to.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he took the cyanide, and he died right there at the phone, because it-- instant, it works instant.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By then, the Jewish gemeinde-- like the one that's now in Wilshire.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You have something, a Jewish Institution.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What the name?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Federation.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
